common.desc:
A powerful piece of equipment that is slowly unsealed based on the wielder's power. Based on the current character's level, the seal will be undone in stages at #cLv. 30/50/70/100#.

Lv. 30+: STR +3, DEX +3, DEF +51
Lv. 50+: STR +5, DEX +5, DEF +69
Lv. 70+: STR +15, DEX +15, DEF +165, Max HP/MP +150
Lv. 100+: STR +25, DEX +25, DEF +195, Max HP/MP +200, Star Force +15
